    "For the purpose of our data collection, we set the launcher to horizontal 30 and vertical 50 for forehand clear.",
    "We set the launcher to horizontal 15 and vertical 30 for right-handers performing the backhand drive.",
    "For left-handers, we adjusted the settings to horizontal 45 and vertical 30.",
    "This allowed us to target specific areas on the court.",
    "As mentioned earlier in the Dataset Design section, a total of three cameras were used to record movements from the front, side, and whole views to obtain information on the participant's stroke."
